config XIAOMI_PERF_HELPER
	tristate "Xiaomi perf helper"
	depends on PROC_FS && SYSFS
	help
	  Reconstructed Xiaomi perf_helper module.

	  The original vendor module exposes perflock, MIMD reclaim, and scheduler
	  assistance interfaces and depends on sched-walt. This reconstruction
	  preserves the visible ABI and user-facing nodes while keeping recovered
	  runtime policy conservative.
